data.description: Beautiful ''Julia'' Model in Verano (PGA Village) just like New! Why build when you can get this home still under the 1st year builder warranty. Features CBS Construction, Flat tile Roof, paver driveway, Transitional Exterior, hurricane impact windows & doors.  Hosts 3 BR's, 2 BA's, 2 CG & spacious covered lanai with Lake View! Fabulous Open floor plan, tile in main areas, Great Room, Volume ceiling & natural lighting. Gorgeous kitchen includes White Cabinets, Stainless steel appliances with Wall Oven, cook top, hood, microwave, large Island with quartz counter tops & walk in Pantry. Custom electric window treatments.  All it needs is your personal touch. Nothing to change - come in and decorate the way you want. Verano feels like a Resort offering something for everyone! HOA includes:Recreation clubhouse Talavera, lawn care, exterior pest control, cable, high speed internet, alarm monitoring & manned gated security. PGA Verano is a resort style community with 27 pickle ball courts, tennis courts, fitness centers with state of the art equipment, indoor and outdoor pools, sauna, and dog park. Exceptional Talavera Social Club 19,000 sq ft. New additional Gym fit bit technology & resistants pool. There is a golf cart path to the PGA Golf Club which offers 3 Public Championship Golf Courses and Private Course (membership optional). Located minutes from Shopping, Restaurants, Activities, Entertainment & Even Home of the New York Mets Spring Training. Only 45 Minutes from Palm Beach Airport and a growing area. The Treasure Coast has beautiful Waterways for the Beach, Fishing & Boating. Due to the location of the Treasure Coast the Weather is delightful!
